```
Better is to let the compiler count for you:
```
void clearScreen()
{
   static const char CLEAR_SCREEN_ANSI[] = &quot;\e[1;1H\e[2J&quot;;
   write(STDOUT_FILENO, CLEAR_SCREEN_ANSI, sizeof(CLEAR_SCREEN_ANSI)-1);
